		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
				<h1 class="firstHeading">Wiki Guidelines</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From GraffeWiki</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>This page will outline the guidelines and rules of Graff&euml;'s Wiki. For the most part, the rules of the wiki follow those listed in the forum rules.
</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents"><tr><td><div id="toctitle"><h2>Contents</h2></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Restricted_Content"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Restricted Content</span></a></li>
